{"tid":1102832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今早遭強制出境往香港　台媒引述倡「武統」學者李毅：我一秒鐘都不想待在台灣","createTime":"2019-04-12T03:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T12:27:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"99caf81eff96d22a12e32046f7679fdec328e8cc","tid":1102832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190412/s00004/98a876c2aeb2a336f463ca82474522c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190412%2Fs00004%2F98a876c2aeb2a336f463ca82474522c0.jpg&h=92f2270a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼓吹「武統」台灣的大陸旅美學者李毅受中國和平統一促進會邀請訪台演講，台灣移民署昨稱李毅持觀光簽證入境，不得發表演說，已廢止李毅入境許可及限令昨天出境。移民署今日稱，李毅未依限令離境，移民署人員上午7時25分執行強制出境，李毅於桃園機場登機離境往香港。<br />\n<br />\n李毅登機前向傳媒稱，對台灣當局做法表示理解，自言一切都很好。他續說，不知此行被安排參與遊行，原本想上玉山，到墾丁游泳。台灣《聯合報》則引述李毅得悉要離台後表示，「我一秒鐘都不想待在台灣，我想馬上就走！」<br />\n<br />\n移民署表示，依規定大陸地區人民以觀光事由訪台，不得參加政治性質公眾活動如遊行、不得接受邀請發表演說，依「大陸地區人民來台從事觀光活動許可辦法」規定，廢止入境許可並限令出境。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）"},{"pid":"0a73ca6c1da1bc57a4daba5ea59b1300831b7e8b","tid":1102832,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸旅美學者李毅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要去香港, 唔掟返美國?"},{"pid":"20b975d09ad1bd09a8aafe4c5436ee55b68ef17e","tid":1102832,"uid":82938,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"0a73ca6c1da1bc57a4daba5ea59b1300831b7e8b","tid":1102832,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸旅美學者李毅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要去香港, 唔掟返美國?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"香港係大陸了"},{"pid":"8878e15869e2385e6fbcaa3dda5f3b3ab93f5085","tid":1102832,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a73ca6c1da1bc57a4daba5ea59b1300831b7e8b","tid":1102832,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸旅美學者李毅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解要去香港, 唔掟返美國?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"轉機掛"},{"pid":"f23318c072fc4b17676b29883b8e0bf82beadb6e","tid":1102832,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a24dad476f5424cee4468eb6e355e040fdd61c8","tid":1102832,"uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"傻閪過晒鐘都唔走要人捉佢走<br />\n<br />\n之後話唔想留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1334670f208ab5d43425735fa5e08f3354c2db5","tid":1102832,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"唔想留係台灣<br />\n咁你當初去黎做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3a3aa9cf1f13f39e5eb99b5097ba32aefa8327","tid":1102832,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"大陸旅美學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db99215ac156f747df5c4830644878e793a04c5","tid":1102832,"uid":41116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d1334670f208ab5d43425735fa5e08f3354c2db5","tid":1102832,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"唔想留係台灣<br />\n咁你當初去黎做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜係咁<br />\n比人踢走趕走一定會拋返句<br />\n我以後都唔黎<br />\n我都唔係好想喺度"},{"pid":"240e2b93c7781f48f93b267d41971b8acc772105","tid":1102832,"uid":53481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"送舊垃圾嚟香港做乜鳩"},{"pid":"648f44a0ea9eed56bf570276d2def9c9878310c4","tid":1102832,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a73ca6c1da1b